Package: lanagent
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-zeroconf, python3-netifaces
Description: LANAgent network discovery service
 LANAgent scans the local layer-2 network, exposes the collected MAC/IP
 mappings through a JSON API and advertises itself via Zeroconf/mDNS. The
 package ships with an optional systemd service that keeps the scanner
 running continuously and publishes results on the configured port.
